Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你們了 鳴海 平
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過孝之還有兼職吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼宮遙 今天准許從櫸綜合醫院出院
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.01,0:00:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在轉往電話留言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在發信號後留下你的留言 並按井號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請記得每星期一次回來複診
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎二 怎麼了 快上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比預定的要晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽等得不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了好多妳愛吃的東西 等著妳回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機的電源快打開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 突然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水月…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要暫時離開這個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一條新的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定我會永遠遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這枚戒指 請再讓我保存一段時日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水月…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 我好像覺得在醫院的屋頂見到水月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也說給我添了很多麻煩 向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必強忍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法珍惜朋友的人 是無法珍惜任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 不因為朋友珍惜自己而感到高興的人 永遠也不會快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水月是最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們而言比誰都要重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的眼淚 正印證著水月是我們最重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點來就好了 孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 妳以為是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 剛起床 嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛起床？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了嘛 她還在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼茜會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像起床了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 來得太早了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼急的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體有哪裡痛的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳自己注意點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要卿卿我我可以 換個地方好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天還有社團活動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 游泳社
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說最近成績都沒有提高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上她都陪我複習準備白陵的入學考試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可能就是原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害得她不能集中精神練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜自己也知道現在是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會自己管好自己的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為小茜能做到 她才能走到今天來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我認為這不是陪遙複習的緣故哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天妳也很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為身邊有孝之在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧 要快點恢復才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 買東西買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 還差一點點 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近冷氣有點毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看電風扇要多少錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前妳也做過了吧 這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 圖畫書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本？不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是 是 是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳居然撒腿就跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個時候還不熟悉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我真的很受打擊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底有多叫人討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的 我是沒想到居然會是孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 不過那個時候我真的很吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭腦一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時候開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直喜歡孝之了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這～麼大的翻車魚 這裡就有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 我以前和水月來過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙出了事故之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 我的腦子一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試也好 什麼事情變成怎麼樣也無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的我 是她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水月讓我振作起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至甘心連游泳這個夢想也放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠水月 讓我走出了最壞的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡水月嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡水月嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡水月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓妳擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手 手機響了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 今天是晚班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？時間要提早？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 現在馬上的話還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分鐘…不 1小時後不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 大空寺那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 大空寺的事情妳知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你的工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作歸工作 遙是遙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在最重要的 當然是遙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼之後我給妳打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜 妳回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還在複習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 有什麼地方不懂的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 平時打擾妳對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜又要上學又有社團很忙的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意 反正也當做是我自己複習 一石二鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 回來的路上碰到鳴海了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這麼晚了還有兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是工作狂人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也有兼職 但他還是陪了我一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一個人上街還有點害怕 他幫了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 孝之這麼忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是從兼職的空餘中抽出來的戀人的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很愛妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是普通的小子能做到的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 戀人就應該是這樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜真是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過鳴海也變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊出院以後幾乎每天都上門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼職那邊好像也很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能比以前要帥多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我發了一下呆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也很準時哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打擾你們了 我失陪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 電話不要講太長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我是遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事情記得馬上給我打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 孝之先生 遙就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 孝之先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定比我們店的牛排還要好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 不過就算是客套話我也很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我們換個位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 再來一杯吧 孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家都是女人 一個人喝酒也挺無聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽不是有時也陪你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人之間把酒暢談是夢想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 乾杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之送的酒果然與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 以後也不用客氣 來喝兩杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 非常樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃杯不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是顧及著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼還要分手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把你的一切都奪過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能這樣愛著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的哈欠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 不小心睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作很忙 沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會夢占卜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 明天妳能陪我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 放假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 之後有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 明天我也去醫院可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳說不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平時總是專心工作 反正明天也放假
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不行 不過排隊的時候很無聊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說遙一直都很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆我們一起打發時間好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然好久沒去醫院了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是女朋友的複診日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好支持女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況良好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活也順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天妳和鳴海一起來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是 我本來想叫他別來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為擔心我所以也一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了騰出一點時間和妳相聚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很愛妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之非常珍惜我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.59,0:22:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就這樣繼續吧 別勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了 循序漸進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說順利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.44,0:22:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人最重要的是健康呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.81,0:22:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是孝之的事情了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.45,0:23:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白塚站？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想去的話不用勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是我睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.30,0:24:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那時候正好相反哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.05,0:24:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.68,0:24:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.73,0:24:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.42,0:24:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶了好東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.33,0:24:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.51,0:24:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘 我做了肉餡餅來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.18,0:24:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 這是你自己做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然失敗了好多次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.88,0:24:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那個時候原來…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.06,0:24:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然味道不敢保證 今天是紀念日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.18,0:24:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀念日？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.72,0:25:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次給遙做肉餡餅的紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.53,0:25:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.03,0:25:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.45,0:25:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 難吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.85,0:25:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.44,0:25:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 練習果然沒有白費
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.83,0:25:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.88,0:25:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想看到遙高興的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.55,0:25:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.30,0:25:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.28,0:25:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.56,0:25:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.93,0:25:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡吧 我們第一次約會的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.27,0:25:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.28,0:25:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我向孝之告白 開始交往
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.20,0:25:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進展卻並不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.92,0:25:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後是我向遙告白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.61,0:25:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們從頭開始的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.38,0:26:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白陵大 妳能上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.02,0:26:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會花不少時間 絕對能上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.06,0:26:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是遙的夢想啊 圖畫書作家
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.50,0:26:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.86,0:26:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之的夢想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.90,0:26:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想啊 確實有事情想做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.96,0:26:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.19,0:26:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找一份好工作 在背後一直支持遙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.88,0:26:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的工作 時間太不規則了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.06,0:26:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是為了和遙在一起的時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.40,0:26:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和遙在一起 永遠永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.62,0:26:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.45,0:26:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會在放開妳
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.78,0:26:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像詛咒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.40,0:26:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 那是…為了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.79,0:26:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.85,0:26:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.32,0:26:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.87,0:27:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 孝之 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.14,0:27:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.55,0:27:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.05,0:27:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.08,0:27:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 孝之
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.60,0:27:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.52,0:27:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.36,0:27:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.42,0:27:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙


